## Best Options

**Pingvin Share** - Modern WeTransfer alternative

- Clean UI, drag-and-drop uploads
- Password protection, expiry dates, download limits
- Share links publicly or with specific people
- Very lightweight, perfect for old laptop

**Send (Timvisee's fork)** - Mozilla Firefox Send clone

- End-to-end encrypted file sharing
- Set expiry time and download count limits
- Simple, beautiful interface
- Auto-deletes after conditions met

**FileBrowser** - Web-based file manager with sharing

- Browse your files through web UI
- Generate public share links for any file/folder
- Built-in file editor, previews
- Can also work as a private file manager

**XBackBone** - ShareX/Imgur alternative

- Perfect for screenshots and quick file uploads
- Custom domains, short URLs
- API support for automation
- Nice gallery view

